What these tests give you

These tests let you validate locally:

IPS Web delegates supplier selection to VerificationProviderService
Individual-not-found flag is passed into PersonVo
Null supplier path routes to error page
Phone formatting logic works in both normal and Hold Mail beans
Log map formatting works

But for the DB lockout fix, do not stop here. You still need the key tests in:

WeightedSupplierSelectorTest
VerificationProviderServiceImplTest

because the uploaded JSF beans do not contain the actual weighted supplier selection algorithm.
